726842f-a.title: Queens: Hawtree Creek Road - 135th Avenue
726842f-a.text:
Hawtree Creek Road, east side, north of One Hundred Thirty-fifth
Ave. (formerly Hegeman Ave.), showing the Bethel Union Sunday School.
It was used as a school in 1860. In 1873 it was designated District
School No. 6; St. Mathews Lutheran Church in 1922. This building is
not the original structure of 1860.
1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
